                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">1. Introduction</h3>
                <p>Welcome to Happy Talk, a global language learning platform designed to help users improve their communication skills through conversation and cultural exchange. We are committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and the measures we take to keep it secure.</p>

